<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow $$ k = $$ \pm $$ 1 ......(1)
<br><br>and $${2 \over 3}\left( {k - 1} \right) = 0$$ $$ \Rightarrow $$ k = 1 ....(2)
<br><br>From (1) and (2),
<br><br>k = 1

