 } } \right] = \left[ {\matrix{
   8  \cr 
   {64}  \cr 

 } } \right] $$
<br><br>$$\Rightarrow 128(x - y) = 8$$<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow x - y = {1 \over {16}}$$ .... (1)<br><br>and $$128( - x + y) = 64 \Rightarrow x - y = {{ - 1} \over 2}$$ .... (2)<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow $$ No solution (from eq. (1) &amp; (2))

