 } } \right)$$<br><br>$$\therefore$$ $$A{Q^{2021}} = {A^T} = A{A^T}{B^{2021}}\,A{A^T} = I{B^{2021}}I$$<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow A{Q^{2021}}\,{A^T} = {B^{2021}} = \left( {\matrix{
